Package: ggRibo
Type: Package
Title: ggRibo: Ribo-seq periodicity and other single-nucleotide resolution visualizer
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Larry Wu
Maintainer: The package maintainer <larrywu@msu.edu>
Description: This package provides tools for visualizing translated ORFs from Ribo-seq results, particularly focusing on open reading frames. The ggRibo function allows analyzing RNA-seq and Ribo-seq coverage in the genomic context. The ggRibo function also helps visualizing other single-nucleotide resolution (SNR) data together with Ribo-seq data.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0),
    GenomicRanges,
    GenomicFeatures,
    GenomicAlignments,
    Rsamtools,
    ggplot2,
    cowplot,
    grid,
    IRanges,
    dplyr,
    txdbmaker,
    R6,
    BiocParallel

RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/hsinyenwu/ggRibo
BugReports: https://github.com/hsinyenwu/ggRibo/issues
